Company Overview of The Leuthold Group, L.L.C.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
The Leuthold Group, L.L.C. is a research firm. It provides equity, economic and fixed income research. The firm universe includes securities traded on United States Exchanges including ADRs. It also analyzes various industries traded on exchanges around the world. The firm offers proprietary and contrarian research which includes commentary on the stock market and the economy, bond market observations, equity strategies, overall asset mix tactics, and industry-related subject matter. It also uses proprietary databases for doing historical studies. The firm seeks to identify equity leadership trends, both domestically and globally. It provides trend analysis using technical analysis. The firm...
The Leuthold Group, L.L.C. is a research firm. It provides equity, economic and fixed income research. The firm universe includes securities traded on United States Exchanges including ADRs. It also analyzes various industries traded on exchanges around the world. The firm offers proprietary and contrarian research which includes commentary on the stock market and the economy, bond market observations, equity strategies, overall asset mix tactics, and industry-related subject matter. It also uses proprietary databases for doing historical studies. The firm seeks to identify equity leadership trends, both domestically and globally. It provides trend analysis using technical analysis. The firm models employ fundamental, technical, and quantitative factors. It offers financial research, broad sector, industry group analysis, and intrisic valuation studies. The firm offers weekly, monthly and quarterly reports. It caters to institutional clients. The firm was formerly known as The Leuthold Group and Cross Research. The Leuthold Group, L.L.C. was founded in 1981 and is based in Minneapolis, Minnesota.
Detailed Description


